dc_creator_sm: Snohomish County Geographic Information System (GIS), Dept. of Information Services
dc_description_s: The Zoning data set shows the location of area-wide zoning ordinances adopted by the County Council. The information contained in the dataset is used for the planning of future development activities in the County.Zoning features are based on the Integrated Land Records (ILR) and are maintained independently by Planning and Development Services (PDS). The arcs were copied from the ILR and put into the zoning to get a good fit, but some lines may not match perfectly with the Assessor's ilr coverages. This data set is derived from a master source maintained by the data steward and updated routinely.
dc_publisher_s: Snohomish County (WA) Geographic Information System (Snohomish GIS)
